	dprr:hasNoteText "Senator in 39. A probable supplement in line 7 of the SC de Aphrodisiensibus (J. M. Reynolds, Aphrodisias and Rome 57 and 69). Cf. Syme, Historia 4, 1955, 66, on gentes that use the cognomen Plautus. Note the L. Sergius in Cic. Dom. 13.[192]\n" .
